<font face="arial" Size="-1" color="caffb0"><b>I know some of this has been mentioned before.

*1*

If you need a sit/stand button just drag the sit/stand button from main screen onto the shortcut button you desire. (if you have linked a button to ex. walk forward , that button is a stupid choice , I know from experiance hehe)

*2*

Also you can make a break spell button fearly easy to save that mana you was just about to use when the mob died or was near detah and the tanks could finish it easy.
Make a duck button on shortcut that ducks you and then put you up again incase you need to flee :)

*3*

If you are pulling and is getting half the zone by accident , be a hero take them away to zone or just die alone saving all you comrades. (I am not pulling hehe)

Glorindar
